ŚIn memory of Ben Cohen, 1915 - 2016.
surgeon and bibliographer
and Myrtle IM Cohen, 1914 - 1987,
SRN and St Pancras Councillor, who lived nearby
20"Ü
ŚThe Sorbus tree in the North side of the garden
was planted in memory of
Sir Terence Rattigan, CBE (1911-1977)
by David Suchet CBE
on 22nd May 2012"×
